-- Denormalized lookup of parent workflow description.
-- Formula for IsStepOfDescription - parse error: Unexpected character '!' at position 15
-- Original: =INDEX(Workflows!{{Description}}, MATCH(WorkflowSteps!{{IsStepOf}}, Workflows!{{WorkflowId}}, 0))

-- Denormalized lookup of parent workflow external identifier.
-- Formula for IsStepOfIdentifier - parse error: Unexpected character '!' at position 15
-- Original: =INDEX(Workflows!{{Identifier}}, MATCH(WorkflowSteps!{{IsStepOf}}, Workflows!{{WorkflowId}}, 0))

-- Denormalized lookup of assigned role label.
